ere is the data that Facebook collects about you regardless. During the hea=
rings, lawmakers focused largely =E2=80=94 if not exclusively =E2=80=94 on =
the former category. But by the the end of Wednesday=E2=80=99s harder-edged=
 hearing, it became clear that the latter category was not nearly as well u=
nderstood. And given its secretive nature, it=E2=80=99s worth much more scr=
utiny.</div><div style=3D"margin: 0;" class=3D"revue-p">As Ben Thompson <a =
