uestioning touched on privacy, Zuckerberg immediately emphasized that Faceb=
ook gives users tools to control who sees their data. It was a quite clever=
 =E2=80=94 and effective =E2=80=94 sleight of hand: the questions were abou=
t the data Facebook owns about each user, but Zuckerberg=E2=80=99s answers =
were about content you upload to Facebook.=E2=80=9D</div><div style=3D"marg=
in: 0;" class=3D"revue-p">We introduced this issue in <a href=3D"http://em.=
