et=3D"_blank">yesterday=E2=80=99s newsletter</a>, amid the discussion of Co=
ngress=E2=80=99 pressure on Facebook to explain how it tracks users around =
the web. But let=E2=80=99s drill down a bit further.</div><div style=3D"mar=
gin: 0;" class=3D"revue-p">The story begins with Rep. Joe Kennedy, who <a h=
