/h6/5AERylSNVCCwj1pUwpeO2QtNYDiK-2FZC7X9T0SXzgzbNi13rDUr-2FEl-2BH9yy3dLGsCd=
PQKR8ggAn2qy-2Fg0A3upzDfuNrYG2JtNW3ncTFlb8izJoP1P-2FdK4FhAATXpZ1vw5Q88goYIZ=
VfR-2FjeJtLxkj6A-3D-3D" style=3D"color: #8b9dc3" target=3D"_blank">pushed Z=
uckerberg into acknowledging</a> the existence of what are commonly called =
=E2=80=9Cshadow profiles.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0=E2=80=9CI don=E2=80=99t understand=
 how users then own that data,=E2=80=9D Kennedy said. In the Atlantic, Alex=
is Madrigal called it <a href=3D"http://em.getrevue.co/mpss/c/DAE/1EoYAA/t.=
