ines for valuable targeting information=E2=80=94and the data that Facebook =
quietly collects around the web, gathers from physical locations, and infer=
s about users based on people who have a similar digital profile. As the jo=
urnalist Rob Horning <a href=3D"http://em.getrevue.co/mpss/c/DAE/1EoYAA/t.2=
gl/Ud2-rwTIQ46KsmIQW7QVCA/h8/VE2atosPJwyp5yA4oN-2FSah-2BIMdzgj-2F66hV9XUCK5=
