C5l-2BgqK9ZaWVLhjbPfaUw7LeSyw2mBiG4ITNtQ-3D-3D" style=3D"color: #8b9dc3" ta=
rget=3D"_blank">pointed out</a> that Facebook builds shadow profiles so tha=
t when you create an account, it knows just who your friends are, and recom=
mend them on your first login. Quickly connecting you to your friends and f=
amily means you will spend more time on Facebook.=C2=A0</div><div style=3D"=
margin: 0;" class=3D"revue-p">If you don=E2=80=99t have a Facebook account,=
 you don=E2=80=99t have control over this data: your friends gave it away o=
n your behalf when they agreed to upload their contacts to Facebook =E2=80=
=94 often <a href=3D"http://em.getrevue.co/mpss/c/DAE/1EoYAA/t.2gl/Ud2-rwTI=
